                Successus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> nostri <lb n="2"/>verna fecit sibi et co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iu</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>gi su<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Pomponi<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Ingenu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>bene merenti inconpara<lb break="no" n="5"/>bili <note>sic</note> amantissim<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> et conserba<lb break="no" n="6"/>trici <note>sic</note> cell<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>es</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> meaes <note>sic</note> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> vixit annis <lb n="7"/>mecum X sibi et suis libertis liber<lb break="no" n="8"/>tabusque posterisque eorum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 4/5: Palmieri, AE 1986: inconpa/rabili; Z. 5: Palmieri: anatissime; Z. 7/8: AE 1986: libert/abusque.</p>
